FBIS4-57077 "drlat093__a94009" FBIS-LAT-94-093-A Daily Report 10 May 1994 ANNEX Brazil Nuclear Commission Registered as Environmental NGO Nuclear Commission Registered as Environmental NGO PY1005215394 Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL in Portuguese 10 May 94 p 6 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY PY1005215394 Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL Portuguese BFN [From the "JB Report" column by Teodomiro Braga: "Nuclear NGO"] [Text] Sidney de Miguel, PV [Green Party] deputy for Rio Grande do Sul, has discovered that the National Nuclear Energy Commission [CNEN] is registered as a nongovernmental organization in the National Registry of Environmental Organizations. As an NGO, the CNEN, which is responsible for the country's nuclear policy, might have access to environment preservation funds.
